{"tid":542714,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"蘋果將中國 iCloud 交予貴州市政府營運","createTime":"2018-01-27T17:51:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-28T04:48:23.000Z","uid":156901,"like":3,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"401b0a9039958744d7ed465284988c698ad64a37","tid":542714,"uid":156901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T17:51:22.000Z","msg":"蘋果將 iCloud 中國帳戶交予 &quot;雲上貴州&quot; 管理，而雲上貴州側屬于貴州市<span style=\"color: red;\">政府全資擁有</span>，並於2月28日開始生效。正常黎講此事只影響 iCloud 的中國用家，但可能會有部份經常往返內地的香港用戶都會受到影響。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/28/015048_343133833739db0554723f2f78acfdde.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F28%2F015048_343133833739db0554723f2f78acfdde.jpg&h=71c89f8d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0ab9fae36c90ba0d2330c2281a8f758df9511077","tid":542714,"uid":29606,"like":2,"dislike":8,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T19:40:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6fa9e569675e0c06d5da8cf4ae3e1d4679c9da83","tid":542714,"uid":67346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0ab9fae36c90ba0d2330c2281a8f758df9511077","tid":542714,"uid":29606,"like":2,"dislike":8,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T19:40:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T20:04:06.000Z","msg":"你個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ade896ab21adae14972e098e92f7159996548b53","tid":542714,"uid":156901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T04:47:45.000Z","msg":"LM"},{"pid":"aeb02798a246cf5e32e6fec78718f1bd56ba62ad","tid":542714,"uid":28563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T04:48:23.000Z","msg":"蘋果死忠不願面對"}]}